# gen59 (C5): best-effort over the blank wall. "what is <X>?" reuses the KB
# description path instead of falling back when X is known.
> Socrates is a man
< Learned: man(socrates).
> Socrates is a mortal
< Learned: mortal(socrates).
> what is Socrates?
< socrates is a man; socrates is a mortal.
> what is a_flamingo?
< I don't know anything about a_flamingo.
